import torch
from transformers import pipeline
#from datasets import load_dataset

device = "cuda:0" if torch.cuda.is_available() else "cpu"

pipe = pipeline(
  "automatic-speech-recognition",
  model="openai/whisper-base",
  chunk_length_s=30,
  device=device,
)
